{
  "texts": [
    "The random algorithm serves as a control to benchmark the sophistication and efficiency of the proposed methods.",
    "Additionally, we utilize a test program developed with the assistance of a domain expert, designed to possess a predetermined WCET, allowing us to gauge our algorithms' accuracy in real-world scenarios.",
    "This comparative study is critical for illustrating the relative strengths and weaknesses of each approach, providing a view of their performance metrics against simple yet universally applicable algorithms, and establishing their validity in accurately predicting WCET in straightforward to complex scenarios.",
    "Additionally, we developed a program, guided by a domain expert, to simulate the 6-DOF case study.",
    "We used this program to apply our RL algorithms and evaluate their performance in estimating WCET."
  ]
}